Collection.Description: Manages global metabase properties that determine how IIS operates
Manages inheritable metabase properties for Web sites and Web virtual directories.
Manages the metabase properties that control FTP sites and FTP virtual directories.
Manages metabase properties that apply to a specific Web virtual server, and to set inheritable metabase properties for virtual directories, Web directories, and Web files.
Manages metabase properties that apply to a specific FTP server and to set inheritable metabase properties for FTP virtual directories.
Manages metabase key values that apply to a file in a Web directory for a Web server.
Is used to set metabase properties that apply to one or more Web directories for a Web server.
Manages metabase properties that apply to one or all virtual directories for a Web site.
Manages metabase properties that apply to one or all FTP virtual directories for an FTP server.
Maps client certificates to Windows user accounts.
